########### Git Intro ##########
you can install git by this command:
# apt install git

there are 3 setting in git: 1- system 2- user 3- project

- system:
# git config --system

- User:
# git config --global

- Project:
# git config

-- User Config:
# git config --global user.name "<username>"
this command set username

# git config --global user.email "<email>"
this command set user email

these two is important.

# git config --list
print user git config

# git config user.name
print username

# git config --global core.editor "vim"
this command force git to use vim editor

# git help <command>
perint that command manual

